    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Polygordius arafura sp. nov.: A, antero-ventral view prostomium, paratype NTM W 20941 (1 of 2 on stub); B, lateral view prostomium, paratype NTM W 20941 (2 of 2 on stub); C, lateral view pygidium, paratype NTM W 20941 (1 of 2 on stub); D – E, posterior views pygidium, paratype NTM W 20941 (1 of 2 on stub). For all SEM images white bars equate to scale measurement (e. g. “ 180 µm ”). F, Polygordius arafura sp. nov. distribution – circles (multiple records overplot); Polygordius kiarama sp. nov. distribution – triangles." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/187028/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

